=================
Terminology 0.4.0
=================

Changes since 0.3.0:
--------------------

Additions:
    * Add a man page
    * Text reflow
    * Add option to set geometry on start
    * Audio keyboard
    * Inline edje objects

Improvements:
    * Compress backscroll
    * Improve terminal compatibility
    * 256-colors support
    * Selection handling

Fixes:
    * Many bugs fixes
